channel.title: World 1 needs to get 1.1 stuff
channel.description:
i'm playing in world 1, since my home was griefed and turned in what i call "a lag hole", as soon as i get in i lag having 2 fps i got too far and made new chunks spawn, with lil pads and a mine, but i explored all the nether looking for a blaze and all chunks were already created, so there's no fortress to get some blaze rods and nether bricks
don't know how can it be done, maybe expanding the world or making a new nether where to teleport like in w2-w1
